deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Tomorrow, February 15. Order within 4 hrs 28 mins
features: DURABLE & STURDY - 1.6cm thick MDF board and 30mm diameter beech wood legs make the open bookshelf very sturdy and durable. Each shelf can hold at least 80lbs;this material is waterproof, anti-scratch and super easy to clean.

MULTI-PURPOSE SHELVING - The design of this bookshelf is modern and simple, which can well decorate and beautify the house.You can place the shelving in the living room to display any crafts and decorations, in the study to store books or on the balcony for potted plants.

VERSATILE OPEN SHELF - Our storage shelves stand can be used not only as bookcase, but also a display shelf, storage shelf. The simple design of this bookcase making it a perfect addition to your home office, study, living room, bedroom, and beyond. It can be used alone or with other furniture.

FREE COMBINATION - We offer a rich choice of models. You can freely combine any number of bookshelves as you need;The tall and slim profile can 2 or 3 shelves to be combined together at the same time to form the perfect display case.

EASY TO ASSEMBLE - Installation of the bookshelf is a piece of cake!!Simply assemble each layer of boards and tighten them with solid wood legs to complete the installation.At the same time, we will provide you with excellent pre-sales and after-sales service.
body.description: IBUYKE Wooden Open Bookcase Floor standing bookcase This bookcase is a modern and elegant storage solution perfect for any home or office. It features beech wood legs and oak finish MDF to complement any decor. Simple white and wood color design is the perfect decoration for your home, bringing you a comfortable and cozy feeling. Multiple models can be freely combined, suitable for anywhere in your home, living room, bedroom, study, kitchen or entryway. Minimalist design - fits almost any style Keeps your books organized EASY TO ASSEMBLE - can be installed in minutes without tools

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice and sturdy! The best bookcase for storage
reviews.reviewText: This bookcase is really well made and it was fairly simple to put together. The instructions were easy to follow and thoroughly written. I got this for storage purposes and its perfect for this purpose because it will fit a lot of your stuff while keeping it all organized. I love the look of it also and goes well with almost any decor. It's rather heavy too and this helps make it nice and sturdy and you won't need to worry about it tipping over. So happy I got this, just wish I had more for a cohesive look. Highly recommend!!
